@Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5044

GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/posts
Accept: application/json

###

POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "A new post from Api.http",
  "content": "This request hits the controller, service, repository, and SQLite database."
}

###

POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/posts/1/comments
Content-Type: application/json

